.TH "flash_wait_op" 9 "flash_wait_op" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
flash_wait_op \- wait for a flash operation to complete
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" flash_wait_op
.BI "(struct adapter *adapter "  ","
.BI "int attempts "  ","
.BI "int delay "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "adapter" 12
the adapter
.IP "attempts" 12
max number of polls of the status register
.IP "delay" 12
delay between polls in ms

Wait for a flash operation to complete by polling the status register.
